      <title>微软股价因云计算增长预测令人失望而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/microsoft-cloud-fuels-stronger-than-expected-revenue-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软股价出现两年来最大跌幅，此前该软件制造商预测季度云计算收入增长将放缓，反映出该公司难以快速上线数据中心以满足人工智能服务的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/microsoft-cloud-fuels-stronger-than-expected-revenue-growth</guid>
